org.hps.record.triggerbank

Class SSPData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.record.triggerbank.AbstractIntData
      • org.hps.record.triggerbank.SSPData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericObject

    public class SSPData
extends AbstractIntData
    Parses the trigger bank information in the SSP trigger bank and converts it into SSPCluster and SSPTrigger objects.
